nodemon = package that monitor changes in the project and don't need to restart the nodejs server over again to see changes.
To run:
npm run start-watch

package.json file contains scripts (like test and start-watch)
it also contains dependencies
and also devDependencies which is only installed on debug mode; on release mode, don't install. (automatically)



