How to update my firebase website / How to test changes before deploying website?
https://stackoverflow.com/questions/40254475/how-to-update-a-file-that-i-deployed-to-firebase-hosting/40263930#40263930


My website is: 
https://my-website-e61fe.firebaseapp.com/


$ firebase serve
That saved the current directory and creates temporary local website that you can view.
It is recommended before using 
$ firebase deploy
because it uploads the entire folder.

